		}

				error 2000
			}
		}

			sort `use' `by'
			if "`standar'"!="" {

local cdf = r(N) - 1

local pval=chiprob(`cdf',`pchi')

				  */ (`irr'-`IRR')^2/`virr') /*

quietly summ `irr' in 1/`df'
local cdf = r(N) - 1
				*local mval=chiprob(`dfm1',`mchi')
local mval=chiprob(`cdf',`mchi')

local dfm1 = `cdf'

		*/ "    " %9.0g `wgt' in gr " `r(label)'"
